  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The main objective this project is the development of a measurement tool. This consists of
      construct and validate a questionnaire to conduct a quantitative assessment of knowledge and
      individual conceptions of cancer enrolled in CM1 and CM2 (9-11 years).
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      -  exper judges by DELPHI method for content validity

        -  pre-testing for appearence validity

        -  testing for construct validity
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
